	* version.h (VERSION), configure.ac Upgraded to version 2.9.13

	* queryfeature.c (panoProjectionFeaturesQuery): Mercator is 179
	vfov max.

	* file.c (CREATED_BY_PSD): This constant needs to be ODD in length

