	2006-01-20  dmg  <dmgerman@uvic.ca>

	* Makefile.am (bin_PROGRAMS): Added PTtiff2psd.

	* PTblender.c (main): Freed pointers. Added call to
	VerifyTiffsAreCompatible.  Added include to PTcommon.h

