2003-12-12 17:32:07  brunopostle  (brunopostle)

	* PixMap.c, PixMap.h, filter.r, makefile.mac, pict.c, shell_mac.c,
	sys_mac.c, sys_mac.h: Extra files required for mac compilation
	as distributed by Helmut Dersch.

